textAnnotations.description:
DEAD MAN TALKING
Hang up and drive. End or conversation.
Lell phones and
sale driving don't
mix. Motorists who
talk on the phone
while driving are
four times more
likely to be involved
TALK
in a crash.
- Save a Life
Texas Deportment of Tronsportation
